"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The director of the National Counterterrorism Center, Joe Kent, says that Trump started a conflict because of pressure from Israel and its strong supporters in America. The deaths of Larijani and the leader of the Basij force have not been confirmed by Iran.\",            \"english_title\": \"Conflict and Unconfirmed Deaths\",            \"translated_version\": \"El director del Centro Nacional de Contraterrorismo, Joe Kent, dice que Trump comenz\u00f3 un conflicto por presi\u00f3n de Israel y sus fuertes seguidores en Am\u00e9rica. Las muertes de Larijani y el l\u00edder de la fuerza Basij no han sido confirmadas por Ir\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conflicto y Muertes No Confirmadas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A jury decided that Kouri Richins killed her husband in March 2022 by giving him a drink with fentanyl, a powerful drug, in it.\",            \"english_title\": \"Jury Finds Wife Guilty\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un jurado decidi\u00f3 que Kouri Richins mat\u00f3 a su esposo en marzo de 2022 d\u00e1ndole una bebida con fentanilo, una droga poderosa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Jurado Encuentra a Esposa Culpable\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Severe weather is affecting the US from one side to the other, with both very hot and very cold temperatures.\",            \"english_title\": \"Extreme Weather in US\",            \"translated_version\": \"El clima severo est\u00e1 afectando a los EE.UU. de un lado a otro, con temperaturas muy calientes y muy fr\u00edas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Clima Extremo en EE.UU.\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president made comments after Israel claimed it had killed Iran's security chief, Ali Larijani, in an attack. Some bodies were so badly injured that they could not be recognized, according to forensic sources.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President Comments on Attack\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. hizo comentarios despu\u00e9s de que Israel afirm\u00f3 haber matado al jefe de seguridad de Ir\u00e1n, Ali Larijani, en un ataque. Algunos cuerpos estaban tan da\u00f1ados que no se pod\u00edan reconocer, seg\u00fan fuentes forenses.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. Comenta sobre Ataque\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Moldova has declared a 15-day state of alert in the Dniester river area as a safety measure.\",            \"english_title\": \"Moldova Declares Alert\",            \"translated_version\": \"Moldavia ha declarado un estado de alerta de 15 d\u00edas en el \u00e1rea del r\u00edo Dni\u00e9ster como medida de seguridad.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Moldavia Declara Alerta\"        }    ]}"